snippet.title: PlayStation Experience 2015: Destiny: The Taken King - Sparrow Racing League Reveal Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/games/destiny-2/?emcid=or-1s-412983

Starting on December 8th, enter the Sparrow Racing League. Compete against your friends on Venus and Mars to earn all-new rewards. Become a racing Legend. 

Learn more about Destiny: The Taken King and buy the Legendary Edition at https://www.destinythegame.com/taken-king/wheretobuy

Keep up with all of the latest information by following us on Facebook (https://www.facebook.com/DestinyTheGame) and on Twitter (@DestinytheGame and @Bungie).
